**Story**
Once opon a time in a forest. There lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the banks of a
river. In the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife... One day the crocodile came to the banks 
of the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back to
the next day as he loved them. As the days passed by the crocodile and the monkey became good friends
One day the monkey sent some fruits for the crocodiles wife . She had the fuits and liked them, but was jealous 
as she did not like the crocodile spending time with the monkey. She told her husband,"if the fruits are so 
juicy, i wonder how much the monkey's heart woukd be. Get me the heart of the monkey". The crocodile was not 
willing to kill his friends but had no choice.